snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP SUES AMBER HEARD, NO PIRATES, MISANDRIST CULTURE WAR IS SHAMELESS
snippet.description:
In 2016, they divorced. But in 2018, Heard gave false statement in METOO, defaming Johnny Depp as an abuser and destroying his career. But now, Depp sues her for defamation. It's time, we stop ostracizing people for their personal matters and leave justice to the Justice League..... sorry, to the Law and Courts.
